@startuml DarQuran_Live_Simple_Flow

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam shadowing false

title 📱 DarQuran Live Streaming - Flux Visuel Simple

!define STEP(x) <size:16><color:white><back:#4CAF50> x </back></color></size>

' === ÉTAPES VISUELLES ===

rectangle "👨‍🏫 **Enseignant**" as teacher #E3F2FD {
}

rectangle "🎮 **OBS Studio**" as obs #FFF3E0 {
    note: Configuration:\nrtmp://server:1935/live/{key}
}

rectangle "🔧 **API Spring Boot**" as api #E8F5E8 {
    note: Gestion sessions\nAuthentification\nNotifications
}

rectangle "📡 **NGINX Server**" as nginx #FFEBEE {
    note: RTMP → HLS\nPort 1935 → 8081
}

rectangle "👨‍🎓 **Élèves**" as students #F3E5F5 {
    note: Angular WebApp\nPlayer HLS
}

rectangle "💾 **Base Données**" as database #F5F5F5 {
    note: PostgreSQL + Redis + MinIO
}

' === FLUX AVEC ÉTAPES ===

teacher --> api : STEP(1) **Créer Session**\nPOST /api/live/sessions\n{Title, StreamKey, AccessType}

api --> database : STEP(2) **Sauvegarder**\nStatus: SCHEDULED\nGénération URLs

teacher --> obs : STEP(3) **Configuration**\nURL RTMP + StreamKey\nCodecs H.264/AAC

obs --> nginx : STEP(4) **Streaming RTMP**\nFlux vidéo temps réel\nIngestion Port 1935

nginx --> nginx : STEP(5) **Conversion HLS**\nSegments .ts (1 sec)\nPlaylist .m3u8

teacher --> api : STEP(6) **Démarrer Live**\nPOST /sessions/{id}/start\nStatut: LIVE

api --> database : STEP(7) **Notifications**\nEmail aux élèves\n(selon section/rôle)

students --> api : STEP(8) **Accès Sessions**\nGET /sessions/my-section\nFiltrage permissions

students --> nginx : STEP(9) **Lecture HLS**\nGET /hls/{streamKey}.m3u8\nPlayer vidéo Angular

students --> api : STEP(10) **Chat Interactif**\nPOST /sessions/{id}/comments\nCommentaires temps réel

teacher --> api : STEP(11) **Fin Session**\nPOST /sessions/{id}/end\nStatus: ENDED

nginx --> database : STEP(12) **Enregistrement**\nUpload MP4 vers S3\n(si activé)

' === ANNOTATIONS ===

note top of nginx
  **🔄 Conversion Automatique**
  RTMP (OBS) → HLS (Navigateur)
  Latence: ~5 secondes
  Qualité adaptative
end note

note bottom of api
  **🔐 Sécurité**
  JWT Authentication
  Rôles: ADMIN/PROF/ÉLÈVE
  Sections: HOMME/FEMME
  Access: INTERNAL/EXTERNAL
end note

note right of database
  **💽 Stockage**
  • Sessions & Métadonnées
  • Commentaires Chat
  • Cache utilisateurs
  • Enregistrements MP4
end note

' === LÉGENDE SIMPLE ===
legend bottom
  **🎯 Technologies Clés:**
  • **Frontend:** Angular + HLS Player
  • **Backend:** Spring Boot + PostgreSQL + Redis
  • **Streaming:** NGINX RTMP + FFmpeg
  • **Protocols:** RTMP (ingestion) + HLS (diffusion)
  • **Security:** JWT + Role-based permissions
end legend

@enduml